videos.description: Tyler Cook throws the no-look bounce pass to Jack Nunge for a two-handed dunk for Iowa.
videos.headline: Iowa's Cook no-look to Nunge for dunk

videos.description: Jordan Bohannon's 3-point jumper in transition off a pass from Luka Garza.
videos.headline: Iowa's Bohannon swishes a 3-pointer

videos.description: Nick Weiler-Babb throws a quick pass to Soloman Young who scores a left-handed layup for the Cyclones.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Young scores bank shot layup

videos.description: Lindell Wigginton hits a jumper from the free throw line to electrify the Iowa State crowd.
videos.headline: Iowa State Wigginton swishes the step-back jumper

videos.description: Jack Nunge's pass deflection ignites the fast break for Iowa then finishes the play with a slam dunk.
videos.headline: Iowa's Nunge throws it down on the fast break

videos.description: Cameron Lard hits the layup off the pass from Hans Brase for the Cyclones.
videos.headline: Iowa State executes high-low to Lard for layup

videos.description: Cameron Lard gets the feed from Hans Brase and connects on the dunk and-1.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Lard muscles dunk for the Cyclones
